<div class="fn" id="TFN1">
<sup>a</sup><p class="display-inline" id="P52"><em>n</em>Gel = cross-linked caprolactone core. EG = (–O–CH<sub>2</sub>–CH<sub>2</sub>–) and <em>d</em>-EG = (–O–CD<sub>2</sub>–CD<sub>2</sub>). VL = (–O–(CH<sub>2</sub>)<sub>4</sub>–CO–). <em>t</em>BuCL = (–O– (CH<sub>2</sub>)<sub>2</sub>–CH(C(CH<sub>3</sub>)<sub>3</sub>)–(CH<sub>2</sub>)<sub>2</sub>–CO–). IBU = ibuprofen.</p>
</div>
<div class="fn" id="TFN2">
<sup>b</sup><p class="display-inline" id="P53">Relative mass-average molar mass (<em>M</em><sub>w</sub>).</p>
</div>
<div class="fn" id="TFN3">
<sup>c</sup><p class="display-inline" id="P54">Small-angle neutron scattering estimate by Pedersen’s model in <em>d</em>-THF.</p>
</div>
<div class="fn" id="TFN4">
<sup>d</sup><p class="display-inline" id="P55">Light scattering GPC in THF.</p>
</div>
<div class="fn" id="TFN5">
<sup>e</sup><p class="display-inline" id="P56">Small-angle neutron scattering estimate by the Zimm plot in <em>d</em>-THF.</p>
</div>
